#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:14
msgid "Alpha operations"
msgstr "Operacions d'alfa"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:16
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Contingut"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:18
msgid ""
"This is Frei0r `alpha0ps <http://www.mltframework.org/bin/view/MLT/"
"FilterFrei0r-alpha0ps>`_ - Display and manipulation of the alpha channel."
msgstr ""
"Aquest és l'`alpha0ps <https://www.mltframework.org/plugins/FilterFrei0r-"
"alpha0ps/>`_ de Frei0r: Mostra i manipula el canal alfa."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:21
msgid "Use this to shrink, grow, threshold and visualize the alpha channel."
msgstr ""
"Utilitzeu-lo per a reduir, augmentar, llindar i visualitzar el canal alfa."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:24
msgid ""
"This plugin can shrink, grow, threshold and invert the alpha channel. It is "
"mainly intended to improve keying edges. It can also display the alpha "
"channel in various ways, to enable quick assessment of the effect."
msgstr ""
"Aquest connector pot reduir, augmentar, llindar i invertir el canal alfa. "
"Està pensat principalment per a millorar les vores de les claus. També pot "
"mostrar el canal alfa de diverses maneres, per a permetre una avaluació "
"ràpida de l'efecte."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:28
msgid ""
"It is cascadable, so for example one can do a soft shrink first and then "
"threshold, which gives a slightly different result than a hard shrink."
msgstr ""
"Treballa en cascada, de manera que, per exemple, primer es pot fer una "
"reducció suau i després un llindar, el qual dóna un resultat lleugerament "
"diferent d'una reducció dura."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:32
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Paràmetres"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:36
msgid "Display"
msgstr "Pantalla"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:37
msgid ""
"what to display. There are seven options: :menuselection:`Image`, :"
"menuselection:`Alpha as gray`, :menuselection:`Gray+red`, :menuselection:"
"`Selection on black`, :menuselection:`Selection on gray`, :menuselection:"
"`Selection on white` and :menuselection:`Selection on checkers`. which lets "
"the unchanged input image through - this plugin is intended to change only "
"the alpha channel..."
msgstr ""
"Què mostrar. Hi ha set opcions: :menuselection:`Imatge`, :menuselection:`Alfa "
"com a gris`, :menuselection:`Gris + vermell`, :menuselection:`Selecció en "
"negre`, :menuselection:`Selecció en gris`, :menuselection:`Selecció en blanc` "
"i :menuselection:`Selecció en quadres`. Permet passar la imatge d'entrada "
"sense canvis: aquest connector està pensat per a només canviar el canal "
"alfa..."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:42
msgid "Display input alpha"
msgstr "Mostra l'alfa d'entrada"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:44
msgid ""
"use input alpha for the display function above. (Check what alpha we are "
"getting on the input)"
msgstr ""
"Utilitzeu l'alfa d'entrada per a la funció de pantalla anterior. (Comproveu "
"quin alfa estem rebent a l'entrada)."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:48
msgid "Operation"
msgstr "Operació"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:50
msgid ""
"select the operation to be done on the alpha channel. Currently there are "
"eight choices: :menuselection:`NO OP`, :menuselection:`Shave`, :"
"menuselection:`Shrink hard`, :menuselection:`Shrink soft`, :menuselection:"
"`Grow hard`, :menuselection:`Grow soft`, :menuselection:`Threshold`, and :"
"menuselection:`Blur`"
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu l'operació que voleu realitzar sobre el canal alfa. Actualment hi "
"ha vuit opcions: :menuselection:`Sense OP`, :menuselection:`Retalla`, "
":menuselection:`Reducció forta`, :menuselection:`Reducció suau`, "
":menuselection:`Augment fort`, :menuselection:`Augment suau`, "
":menuselection:`Llindar` i :menuselection:`Difuminat`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:53
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Shave` try to remove the \"hairy\" stuff, and also shrinks "
"the selection a bit."
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`Retalla` intentarà eliminar les coses «peludes» i també "
"reduirà una mica la selecció."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:56
msgid ""
"The *hard* operations introduce no new values to the alpha channel, so if "
"you have a \"hard\" key (only 0 and 255) it will stay that way."
msgstr ""
"Les operacions *dures* no introduiran valors nous al canal alfa, de manera "
"que si teniu una clau «dura» (només 0 i 255) aquesta seguirà així."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:59
msgid ""
"The *soft* operations will introduce interpolated values, making the edge "
"softer."
msgstr ""
"Les operacions *suaus* introduiran valors interpolats, fent que la vora sigui "
"més suau."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:64
msgid ""
"The shave, shrink and grow operations are quite slow, because they do many "
"conditional operations on each pixel."
msgstr ""
"Les operacions de retallar, reduir i augmentar són força lentes, perquè fan "
"moltes operacions condicionals sobre cada píxel."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:68
msgid "Threshold"
msgstr "Llindar"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:70
msgid "This is only used for the :menuselection:`Threshold` operation."
msgstr "Només s'utilitza per a l'operació de :menuselection:`Llindar`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:74
msgid "Shrink/grow amount"
msgstr "Quantitat de reducció/augment"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:76
msgid "How far the shrinking/growing will extend."
msgstr "Fins on s'estendrà la reducció/augment."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:80
msgid "Invert"
msgstr "Inverteix"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/alpha_manipulation/alpha_operations.rst:82
msgid ""
"Inverts the input alpha channel, transparent will become opaque and vice "
"versa."
msgstr ""
"Inverteix el canal alfa d'entrada, el transparent es tornarà opac i "
"viceversa."

